videos.description: LeBron James shares his thoughts on the new format of the NBA All-Star Game and on what honoring Kobe Bryant meant to everyone.

videos.headline: LeBron: The new format brought out the competitive spirit in everyone

videos.description: Kawhi Leonard talks to Rachel Nichols about what playing with the new ASG format was like, having children from each charity courtside and his emotions after winning the first Kobe Bryant MVP trophy.

videos.headline: Kawhi remembers comparing shot attempts with Kobe

videos.description: Steph Curry loves the new All-Star Game format, passionately debating whether Giannis' block on LeBron James is goaltending.

videos.headline: Steph fired up watching All-Star Game

videos.description: James Harden says he teared up during the pregame ceremony that honored Kobe Bryant and his daughter Gianna. Harden also talks about the ASG's new format and watching Chris Paul throw down an alley-oop.
